Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with language understanding tasks and investigates the grammatical knowledge of pretrained sentence encoders. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the performance of different models and their ability to learn certain phenomena. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with machine learning models. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper discusses the performance of neural network models. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the OpenAI Transformer, which has been used for image captioning tasks.
